trans-unit.source: Represents one, and only one, of three possible properties of a print queue: <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.Location*>, <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.Comment*>, or <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.ShareName*>.
trans-unit.target: 表示一个，且只有一个打印队列的三个可能的属性︰ <> </> *1>， <> </> *1>，或<xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.ShareName*>。</xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.ShareName*>

trans-unit.source: An object of this class is primarily used as a parameter for one of the overloaded <xref:System.Printing.PrintServer.InstallPrintQueue%2A> methods of a <xref:System.Printing.PrintServer>.
trans-unit.target: 此类的对象主要用于作为参数的重载<xref:System.Printing.PrintServer.InstallPrintQueue%2A>方法的一种<xref:System.Printing.PrintServer>。</xref:System.Printing.PrintServer></xref:System.Printing.PrintServer.InstallPrintQueue%2A>之一

trans-unit.source: This method makes it possible to install a print queue while initializing only one of its three major <xref:System.String> properties.
trans-unit.target: 此方法使它能够安装打印队列，同时初始化仅对其中一个其三个主要<xref:System.String>属性。</xref:System.String>

trans-unit.source: Having three separate overloads of the method is not possible because they would have the same signature and no two overloads of a method can have the same signature.
trans-unit.target: 由于它们都将有相同的签名，并且两个重载的方法可以具有相同的签名，具有三个单独该方法的重载不可能。

trans-unit.source: If you want to install a print queue and initialize two or more of its major string properties, there is another overload, <xref:System.Printing.PrintServer.InstallPrintQueue%2A>, that substitutes three <xref:System.String> parameters for the PrintQueueStringProperty parameter.
trans-unit.target: 如果你想要安装打印队列并初始化两个或多个主要的字符串属性，则另一个重载， <xref:System.Printing.PrintServer.InstallPrintQueue%2A>，，替换三个<xref:System.String>PrintQueueStringProperty 参数的参数。</xref:System.String> </xref:System.Printing.PrintServer.InstallPrintQueue%2A>

trans-unit.source: These parameters are used to set the major String properties in this order: <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.ShareName%2A>, <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.Comment%2A>, and <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.Location%2A>.
trans-unit.target: 这些参数用于设置此顺序中的主要的字符串属性︰ <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.ShareName%2A>， <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.Comment%2A>，和<xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.Location%2A>。</xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.Location%2A> </xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.Comment%2A> </xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue.ShareName%2A>

trans-unit.source: Use an empty string for a parameter that corresponds to a property you do not want to initialize.
trans-unit.target: 你不想初始化的属性相对应的参数使用一个空字符串。

trans-unit.source: > [!CAUTION] > Classes within the <xref:System.Printing> namespace are not supported for use within a Windows service or ASP.NET application or service.
trans-unit.target: 1> [!CAUTION]&1;> 类内<xref:System.Printing>命名空间不支持的 Windows 服务或 ASP.NET 应用程序或服务中的使用。</xref:System.Printing>

trans-unit.source: Attempting to use these classes from within one of these application types may produce unexpected problems, such as diminished service performance and run-time exceptions.
trans-unit.target: 尝试使用这些应用程序类型之一中的这些类可能会产生意外的问题，如降低服务性能和运行时异常。

trans-unit.source: If you want to print from a Windows Forms application, see the <xref:System.Drawing.Printing> namespace.
trans-unit.target: 如果你想要从 Windows 窗体应用程序打印，请参阅<xref:System.Drawing.Printing>命名空间。</xref:System.Drawing.Printing>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Printing.PrintQueueStringProperty"></xref> class.
Gets or sets the value of the print queue property that is represented.
trans-unit.target: 获取或设置表示打印队列属性的值。

trans-unit.source: For example, if the <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueueStringProperty.Type%2A> is <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueueStringPropertyType>, the Name might be "Department Supply Room"; but if the <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueueStringProperty.Type%2A> is <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueueStringPropertyType>, the Name might be "Use only A4 size paper with this printer."
trans-unit.target: 例如，如果<xref:System.Printing.PrintQueueStringProperty.Type%2A>是<xref:System.Printing.PrintQueueStringPropertyType>，名称可能"部门提供的空间"; 但是，如果<xref:System.Printing.PrintQueueStringProperty.Type%2A><xref:System.Printing.PrintQueueStringPropertyType>，则名称可能为"使用唯一 A4 大小纸与此打印机。"</xref:System.Printing.PrintQueueStringPropertyType> </xref:System.Printing.PrintQueueStringProperty.Type%2A> </xref:System.Printing.PrintQueueStringPropertyType> </xref:System.Printing.PrintQueueStringProperty.Type%2A>

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.String> with the value of the property.
Gets or sets a value that identifies which of the three possible properties of a print queue is being represented.
trans-unit.target: 获取或设置要表示的是一个值，标识哪些打印队列的三个可能的属性。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Printing.PrintServer.InstallPrintQueue%2A> method of a <xref:System.Printing.PrintServer> uses this information to ensure that the <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueueStringProperty.Name%2A> value is assigned to the correct property of the <xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue> being installed.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Printing.PrintServer.InstallPrintQueue%2A>方法<xref:System.Printing.PrintServer>使用此信息来确保<xref:System.Printing.PrintQueueStringProperty.Name%2A>值分配给的正确属性<xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue>正在安装。</xref:System.Printing.PrintQueue> </xref:System.Printing.PrintQueueStringProperty.Name%2A> </xref:System.Printing.PrintServer> </xref:System.Printing.PrintServer.InstallPrintQueue%2A>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Printing.PrintQueueStringPropertyType"></xref> that specifies the kind of print queue property that is being represented.
trans-unit.target: A <xref href="System.Printing.PrintQueueStringPropertyType"> </xref> ，它指定所表示的打印队列属性的类型。
